</s>
<s id="505:11">
Il faut renforcer les moyens humains les moyens matériels les moyens financiers de l'agence Frontex lui permettre de soutenir de manière plus appuyée les opérations Hermes et les opérations ehm Poséidon.
</s>
<s id="505:12">
Oui il faut des moyens financiers supplémentaires additionnels pour les États membres qui sont confrontés je dirais en premier rang en premier lieu aux /aaux/ ehm flux miga- migratoires ehm accentués ehm que nous connaissons ehm aujourd'hui.
</s>
<s id="505:13">
Et ce sera l'expression financière de notre solidarité.
</s>
<s id="505:14">
Oui il faut ehm nouer des relations de coopération plus étroites avec les États ehm de la rive sud de la Méditerranée les accompagner bien sûr les aider trouver des instruments.
</s>
<s id="505:15">
